ts/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/common/requests/) define the protocol messages for inter-broker communication. The LeaderAndIsr metadata (metadata/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/metadata/LeaderAndIsr.java) and BrokersToIsrs controller (metadata/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/controller/BrokersToIsrs.java) maintain the ISR state in the metadata layer. Log offset management is supported through LogOffsetMetadata (storage/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/storage/internals/log/LogOffsetMetadata.java), LogOffsetSnapshot, and related classes that track commit offsets and high watermark progression."
